Green Mountain Sees Demand Rising for Single-Serve Brewed Coffee

-- B y   D e b a r a t i   R o y
-- 
2011-03-18T17:22:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/green-mountain-sees-demand-rising-for-single-serve-brewed-coffee.html
  Green Mountain Coffee Roasters Inc. (GMCR) 
expects demand to increase for single-serve brewing systems,
said Chris Stevens, a company vice president.  “The company is working hard to keep up with demand,”
Stevens said today during an interview at an industry conference
in  New Orleans .  Waterbury, Vermont-based Green Mountain is the largest
player in the U.S. single-serve coffee market, which generated
almost $2 billion in sales last year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Debarati Roy in Mumbai at 
 droy5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Stroth at 
 sstroth@bloomberg.net  